through and the sound of singing seems almost to come from everywhere at 
once. 
~
Sector city~
Exit southeast 64103
Exit northwest 64101
End


#64103
Name A District Intersection~
Desc This busy little intersection is bustling with peddlers trying to hawk their 
wares and priests denouncing them. To the east comely women beckon while to 
the south temple chimes whistle gently in the wind. To the northwest and 
west roads curve away with the celestial sound of voices in song echoing 
down them and into the heavens. 
~
Sector city~
