Exit southwest 64122
End


#64105
Name Anshio Exit Gate~
Desc To the south droves of people scramble to be the first out of a small 
doublewide gate. Craftsmen with barren carts and full carts alike squabble 
over who will be first for what reason as children rush around them. The 
gate in question is a large one with heavy black oak door and porticullis 
set into the large stone wall that seperates the city from outsiders. 
~
Sector city~
Exit west 64106
Exit northeast 64122
End


#64106
Name Anshio Entrance Gate~
Desc To the south a large gate for those who are entering the city has been set 
