title Kanishi Takes the Bait~
author Reath~
code sayto $n [cynically]What do you know of the perfect weapon? I spent my life honing skills to create an instrument worthy of that title.[he waves towards the door.]
mq3 sayto $n [pausing]No.. stay.
mq5 sayto $n It must be a sign. I was thinking of such a thing today.[he smiles quietly]If you wish, bring some wood for an old man to tinker with? Three logs would be wonderful... but make sure they are the same kind... if you wish to humor me.[hope is plain on his face.]
~
disabled false
last_editor Reath~
last_editdate 1120367726
END

